{"tid":2094041,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"社會法則：多人做就無問題 少人做就係畸形","createTime":"2020-07-04T09:31:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-06T01:29:15.000Z","uid":45652,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2a0c78a8897f4af7d7631dbab7d7d17c1d213790","tid":2094041,"uid":45652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T09:31:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P8NVBuS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP8NVBuS.png&h=e0d99fb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一隻狗風火山林就要局長解釋<br />\n全部狗風火山林就無問題<br />\n七隻狗暗角打鑊就要比人告<br />\n全部狗當街打鑊就無問題<br />\n<br />\n相反 <br />\n<br />\n二百萬人上街霸哂全部馬路無問題<br />\n二百個人上街霸左條行人路就非法集結<br />\n港大幾十個有地位既人出聲就唔強攻<br />\n理大無人出聲就死守強攻<br />\n七一成條街叫香港獨立無問題<br />\n七一比人搜身有光復香港就三年起刑<br />\n<br />\n我地人多不過無組織唔團結<br />\n佢地人少不過有組織專打散黎打"},{"pid":"3b9f864bdd5995041f3efcb1283b78befe36c9bb","tid":2094041,"uid":27416,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T09:34:03.000Z","msg":"法不治眾"},{"pid":"6df1a752e590311d7c06b1802b7e11220be633b1","tid":2094041,"uid":45652,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T09:36:34.000Z","msg":"只要出黎風險高左<br />\n已經可以減一半人<br />\n<br />\n二百萬人都可以唔理<br />\n而家直程為所欲為"},{"pid":"dbe246161b1bccd07327d1ee992e882ec9f9203f","tid":2094041,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T09:44:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"860f29a0f8532dfa843640ab22fc8d5f078f5a6d","tid":2094041,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3b9f864bdd5995041f3efcb1283b78befe36c9bb","tid":2094041,"uid":27416,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":